                content: `<h2>DeftAgile Values</h2> <p>These are the values that are deemed important to both product development and agile engineering teams</p> <p><span>·<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>Customer Centricity</p> <p><span>·<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>Collaboration and Empathy</p> <p><span>·<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>Transparency and Communication</p> <p><span>·<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>Innovation and Flexibility</p> <p><span>·<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>Accountability and Ownership</p> <p><i>&nbsp;</i></p>`,
                pageTitle: 'DeftAgile Values | DeftAgile Guide',
